1
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,320
Greetings, Scorpion King.

2
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:18,360
Here we are, my ghost friends.

3
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:20,480
Why are you angry?

4
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,760
Get away!

5
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:26,800
My ghost brother,

6
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:29,120
why are you so sissy and angry?

7
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,520
Do you think I'll be scared?

8
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,720
Enough.

9
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,040
Scorpion King,

10
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,480
the reason we follow Chief Zhao

11
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,920
is that we are tired
of fighting and killing.

12
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:41,120
We want to quit.

13
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:44,040
The Xianxia Sect has nothing to do
with our Ghost Valley.

14
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,400
So

15
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,840
don't count us in.

16
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:48,960
What a coincidence.

17
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,520
What Chief Zhao likes

18
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:54,120
is your killing skills.

19
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,800
If devils don't kill,
then what do they do?

20
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,240
Farming and collecting rent?

21
00:02:58,320 --> 00:03:01,840
Even Chief Zhao wouldn't dare
to talk to our leader this way.

22
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,520
You brat!

23
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,480
"You brat"?

24
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:22,960
Here is some powder for deodorization.

25
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,920
You wicked woman, how dare you poison him?

26
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,160
Give me the antidote!

27
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,360
How dare you?

28
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,880
In my presence,

29
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:33,720
how could you be rude to our allies?

30
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,440
Give him the antidote.

31
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,800
Yes.

32
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:59,160
Chief Zhao asked everyone here
to wipe out the Xianxia Sect.

33
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,640
He has his reason for that.

34
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:05,440
If you are not willing to do it,

35
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,920
we could just go separate ways

36
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,680
in a peaceful manner.

37
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:11,440
However, in the future,

38
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,440
we could be either friends or foes.

39
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,080
Changing Ghost.

40
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,519
Am I right?

41
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,240
Scorpion King,

42
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:23,000
things are not that bad.

43
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,720
If Chief Zhao wants to wipe out

44
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:27,520
the puny Xianxia Sect,

45
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:30,320
I will just follow his order.

46
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:32,400
That's very good then.

47
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,680
By the way,

48
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,960
I will send Pretty Arhat to go with you,

49
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,680
just in case.

50
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,640
My brothers!

51
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,240
Let's go.

52
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,040
Evil Bodhisattva,

53
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,080
tell Pretty Arhat

54
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,560
to leave some survivors

55
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:55,600
to spread the news.

56
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,080
Spread the news?

57
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,320
To whom?

58
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,640
To the entire martial arts world.

59
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:07,240
The century-long established Xianxia Sect

60
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:09,560
was decimated by the Ghost Valley.

61
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:12,960
I want to see
who can stay aloof hearing that.

62
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,080
Changing Ghost,

63
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:24,880
you rank first in the Ten Devils.

64
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:30,200
Yet you gave up the privileges

65
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:34,320
and served those bastards?

66
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:35,680
How delightful.

67
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:36,960
That is really delightful!

68
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,840
Although that Lunatic Wen is crazy,

69
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:44,280
for better or worse,
he is in the same boat as us.

70
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,720
If we sink,

71
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,440
he won't survive.

72
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:50,360
Since we've already joined
the Ghost Valley,

73
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,600
is going back

74
