a choice?

75
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:58,000
Do you think we can live
if we don't go back?

76
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:02,560
Let's not talk about Wen Kexing first.
That crazy guy is mentally unstable.

77
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:05,200
It's crazy
that those ghosts leaving the valley

78
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:08,920
are enough to turn
the entire world against us

79
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,800
like they're afraid that
this world wouldn't hate us more.

80
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:16,160
If only Gao Chong survived that incident

81
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,960
and brought back his allies
for another war on Mount Qingya--

82
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,960
Nonsense!

83
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,640
How is Zhao Jing different
from that Lunatic Wen?

84
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,960
What Zhao Jing wants is no more than a war

85
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,880
between the Ghost Valley
and those righteous clans.

86
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,160
He wants to kill us and them.

87
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,000
Changing Ghost.

88
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,880
If you serve Zhao Jing as his lackey,

89
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:38,800
you may earn yourself some fame
and have a good ending.

90
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,960
But Happy Ghost and I will not.

91
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:45,120
Our bloody hands

92
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,440
cannot be cleansed.

93
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,440
If we both serve Zhao Jing as his blade,

94
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:54,000
what benefits could we expect in the end?

95
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,280
Lustful Ghost,

96
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:59,480
what's the point
of saying these things now?

97
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:02,200
We have betrayed that Lunatic Wen
and we can't go back.

98
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:04,200
Under Zhao Jing's wings,

99
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:06,560
at least, we have one way out.

100
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:09,080
If you can't accept it,

101
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,920
you could just go back to the Ghost Valley

102
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,120
and beg Lunatic Wen

103
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:18,160
for his mercy.

104
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,200
You haven't been

105
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,240
in the Ghost Valley for long.

106
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,600
I'm afraid you don't know

107
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:30,120
how Lunatic Wen took over
the Ghost Valley.

108
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,200
It's said that

109
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:37,080
when he ascended to power,
in everyone's presence,

110
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:41,960
he ate the former chief
of the Ghost Valley alive,

111
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,840
piece by piece,

112
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,240
which totally frightened everyone.

113
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,600
That's fake.

114
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:54,600
In front of everyone,

115
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:57,760
he peeled off the skin
of the former chief alive.

116
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,480
Chief!

117
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,480
From today on,

118
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:25,640
I'm the supreme!

119
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:38,520
So Mr. Wen met you when he was a kid,

120
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:41,720
but why didn't Grand Master take him back?

121
