Your grand master was occupied
with some important affairs

122
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,840
and couldn't go with those
who were heavily wounded.

123
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,720
So he promised them that in three months,

124
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,600
he would take them back
to the Four Seasons Manor.

125
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,400
But who would have thought

126
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:56,720
that when he went back to that village,

127
00:09:57,400 --> 00:10:00,600
it had been leveled off?

128
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,960
That incident then

129
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:08,280
became a scar that
your grand master secretly bore.

130
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:11,880
When my junior disciple, Qin Jiuxiao,
became an adult

131
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,560
and went through
the ceremony of joining the sect,

132
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,720
