133
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:19,880
I knew then

134
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,960
that he regretted it to such an extent.

135
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,360
They have already been saved,

136
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:28,240
yet you were somehow separated.

137
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,360
What a pity.

138
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,840
It was so close.

139
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,320
Master Wen could have grown up with you.

140
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:37,760
