before you did.

141
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:40,840
But

142
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:44,240
why didn't he admit that he is Zhen Yan?

143
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:47,080
Zhen Ruyu was the adopted son
of Old Zhen of the Healer Valley.

144
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,760
Maybe his family name was "Wen,"

145
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,440
so he might not want to hear "Zhen" again.

146
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:52,880
But why not?

147
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:57,640
The former chief expelled them
from the sect.

148
00:10:58,440 --> 00:11:00,120
What happened to
Hero Zhen's family after that?

149
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,200
-Master.
-Enough, kid.

150
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:04,920
Don't touch a raw nerve.

151
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,840
Look at Wen Kexing.

152
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:08,880
Does he seem like he has been
disciplined by his parents?

153
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,800
Master Ye!

154
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:13,040
Are you saying thatâ€¦

155
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:15,920
Could it be that Hero Zhenâ€¦

156
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:18,880
Maybe the Zhen couple

157
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,480
died long ago.

158
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:24,920
This must be something
he doesn't want to talk about.

159
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,520
If he doesn't mention it,

160
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:29,160
don't bring it up first. Do you hear me?

161
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:32,960
Good kid.

162
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:37,280
It doesn't matter
if he doesn't accept me as his senior.

163
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:40,200
I will always consider him as my junior.

164
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:42,760
I am just sad that

165
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,960
a good person such as Hero Zhen

166
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:47,440
didn't get a good ending.

167
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,440
Master.

168
00:11:49,520 --> 00:11:52,320
Why do good people end up
in the worst way?

169
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:53,320
Father,

170
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,240
Master Long,

171
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:56,160
and the Zhen family.

172
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,920
Even Mr. Rong Xuan

173
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,360
didn't do anything evil.

174
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,960
Destiny is hard to predict.

175
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:03,800
Life is unexpected.

176
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:07,400
All people with emotions suffer.

177
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,960
Not just good guys.

178
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:16,280
Ah Xu, I think your good deeds
kind of paid off.

179
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,160
-You almost--
-Mr. Wen!

180
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,640
No, it's Master Wen.

181
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:23,160
Can I call you that?

182
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:29,800
Old Monster, why are you still here?

183
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:32,040
You can be here, so why can't I?

184
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,720
We're going to the Four Seasons Manor.

185
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,960
Why are you coming with us?

186
00:12:39,040 --> 00:12:42,680
You take your way and I will take mine.
It's none of your business!

187
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,600
I dare go places with extreme danger,

188
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:46,640
let alone a manor.

189
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,720
Fine.

190
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:49,520
The lord of the manor is here.

191
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:52,040
If he accepts your visit,
I will not say otherwise.

192
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:55,240
If Master Ye is willing
to visit our manor,

193
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,720
we'll be pleased to welcome you.

194
00:12:59,560 --> 00:13:02,600
I've long heard the great name
of divine husband-wife physicians.

195
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:06,120
They were both elites of the elites.
What a divine couple they were.

196
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:08,800
Why did they give birth
to such an annoying kid?

197
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,120
What a pity.

198
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,880
But no matter what,

199
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,640
you will always be their child.

200
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:18,280
