203
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,240
Little brat.

204
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:27,760
Tell me your wish.

205
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,840
Listen.

206
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:34,640
The dead can't come back to life.

207
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:37,040
That is the only thing I can't do.

208
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:40,240
I'm afraid there aren't many things
beyond my capability.

209
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,360
Do you have a wish? Just tell me.

210
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:44,120
I will surely help you realize it.

211
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,880
Listen.

212
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,280
I'm not helping you.

213
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,560
This is what you deserve.

214
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:52,720
Wen Kexing.

215
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:54,560
Please tell me your wish.

216
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,240
Otherwise,

217
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:00,160
I'm afraid

218
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:02,480
I won't die in peace.

219
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:11,280
I only have one wish.

220
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:13,480
Cure Ah Xu.

221
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:17,080
If you manage to do so,
all our previous debts are clear.

222
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:19,280
But make sure his life span
is not shortened

223
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,760
and his martial arts remain the same.

224
00:14:24,680 --> 00:14:25,600
You brat!

225
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:27,240
Do you think
that will be difficult for me?

226
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,960
Though I don't have the solution,

227
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,680
I know who does.

228
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:33,680
You guys just stay
in the Four Seasons Manor

229
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:35,000
and wait for my return.

230
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,240
Master Ye.

231
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:37,920
Who are you looking for?

232
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,480
How long shall we wait for you?

233
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:41,600
If even he can't save you,

234
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,120
I willâ€¦

235
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,960
Hey, Old Monster!

236
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:48,080
Ye Baiyi!

237
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,880
He's not like a 100-year-old man at all,

238
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:53,200
but a child when he's in a rush.

239
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,400
What Old Monster meant

240
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:57,320
is your wound is curable, right?

241
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:59,240
He likes to brag a lot.

242
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:02,000
How do I know whether he was about to say,

243
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:04,960
"I will repay you by cutting off my head"
or "I will host your funeral"?

244
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:07,720
Did you hear that?

245
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,400
Your master's wound can be cured!

246
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:11,240
What great news.

247
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,600
Master Ye is very capable.

248
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:14,480
He meant what he said.

249
00:15:15,160 --> 00:15:16,120
We can go home now!

250
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,960
Let's go home!

251
