more vigorous and integrated.

254
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:45,600
I like it so much.

255
00:15:45,680 --> 00:15:47,720
Could you stamp it and give it to me?

256
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,280
You little barbarian.

257
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,720
